My new HUION Kamvas Pro 24 4K! Really happy with it. After working with Wacom products for many years it was time to give a chance to Huion. Couldn't be happier. No heat, no lag, light and easy to configure. The 4K screen looks amazing and supports a wider color range than my regular monitor. Definitely an improvement, and way cheaper than a Cintiq. 100% recommendable!

Mi nueva HUION Kamvas Pro 24 4K! Super contento con ella. Después de usar Wacom toda la vida decidí darle una oportunidad a las Huion, ya que había oído hablar muy bien. No se calienta, no laguea, es ligera y fácil de configurar. La pantalla 4K se ve increíble, mucho mejor que mi monitor, y con más rango de color. Definitivamente una gran mejora, y a un precio muy inferior a las Cintiq equivalentes. 100% recomendable!

Well, don't know if I'm going to finish this. Heck, I don't even know if I'll start. But here's a tentative list just in case. Nobody ask me for these in commissions, so I'll go with some of my favorite characters in comics (other than DC, of course). Cheers! #inktober2023 Belit, Dr Doom and Jean Grey already reserved.

#Inktober 31: Corto Maltese. That's a wrap! Thanks all for watching. It's been a lot of fun, drawing characters I love without seeking for a finished look or detail, just for the sake of drawing. Maybe more next year, maybe not! :)
